  ${
    $d X x y $.  $d A x y $.  $d B y $.  $d H x y $.  $d R x y $.
    crngcom.1 $e |- G = ( 1st ` R ) $.
    crngcom.2 $e |- H = ( 2nd ` R ) $.
    crngcom.3 $e |- X = ran G $.
    $( The multiplication operation of a commutative ring is commutative. $)
    crngcom $p |- ( ( R e. CRing /\ A e. X /\ B e. X )
                                        -> ( A H B ) = ( B H A ) ) $=
      ( vx vy ccring wcel co wceq cv wral wa cring iscring2 pm3.27bi opreq1
      opreq2 eqeq12d rcla42v mpan9 3impb ) CLMZAFMZBFMZABENZBAENZOZUHJPZKPZENZU
